data.description: This 4 bedroom/3.5 bathroom, 3306 sq ft colonial classic has been restored to breathtakingly modern living!  Sitting on almost an acre directly across from Pinecrest Country Club (golf, pool, fine dining, drinks, etc.), this work of art will capture your heart!  As you enter the front door, you will find yourself in an incredible living room with a lovely fireplace that is followed by a study (perfect for working remotely) with built-ins, a separate entrance/exit and half bath. You will transcend to your housewarming party when you continue to the large formal dining, butlers pantry, kitchen, and breakfast room. Upstairs you will find four spacious bedrooms with two living areas and three full bathrooms. This unique property is beautifully maintained with original chandeliers, glass mosaic window, wood shutters, hardwood floors, tile details, bay windows, and high ceilings. Conveniently positioned between Loop 281 & I-20, this location is great for commuters as well.   Call Listing Agent for tour of this home that only gets better in person!
